<paragraph blockId="33.[151,1437,512,1403]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,1341,1367]" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">Etymology.</emphasis>
The name is formed from the Latin words 
<emphasis box="[819,873,1341,1367]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">pilus</emphasis>
, hair and 
<emphasis box="[986,1054,1341,1367]" italics="true" pageId="33" pageNumber="34">cauda</emphasis>
, tail, referring to the richly setose hypopygium of the species.
</paragraph>
